" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/triggeredEvent/triggeredEventBox/tooltip"
msgstr "Si no derrotas a la nave MFK Ace en este tiempo, ¡el transporte escapará!"

